      • allowNavItemsFocus

        protected boolean allowNavItemsFocus()
        Navigation bar entry point to determine if the keyboard/focus behavior should be compatible with screen readers. This additional level of indirection makes it easier to figure out the various locations in the various navigation bar components that enable screen reader friendly behavior.
